  "promptForAI": "Create a complete V60 manual brew coffee timer web application using only HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The app should follow the design system principles from the Fitness Dashboard (rounded corners, card-based layout, purple/blue primary colors, clean minimal aesthetic) but adapted for a coffee brewing context with warm brown/orange accents. \n\nImplement a multi-phase brew timer with circular progress indicator, pour tracking, multiple recipe support, brew history with local storage, and an intuitive mobile-first interface. Include all screens: recipe selection, brew timer, completion, history, and settings.\n\nThe app should have smooth animations, be fully responsive, accessible, and feel like a native mobile app experience. Prioritize user experience during the active brewing process with minimal required interactions and clear visual feedback. Use CSS variables for design tokens to maintain consistency throughout."
